## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **omaveloxolone Skyclarys 2023** = first FDA Friedreich ataxia. Nrf2 activator → 미토콘드리아 + 항산화 paradigm. cross-iag (Nrf2 = inflammation crosstalk). quantum-VQE 의 Nrf2 pocket fit.
2. **elamipretide (SS-31) 2024 pending** = first FDA-pending mitochondrial therapeutic — Barth syndrome (cardiolipin 결핍). cardiolipin-targeted peptide → 미토콘드리아 막 침투. quantum-VQE 의 lipid bilayer + peptide 결합 modeling 한정.
3. **idebenone EU 2015 (Catena/Raxone)** = LHON 첫 승인 (US 미승인). short-chain CoQ10 analog. quantum-VQE 의 호흡쇄 complex I 결합 modeling.
4. **triheptanoin Dojolvi 2020** = first FDA LCFAOD (long-chain fatty acid oxidation disorder). odd-chain triglyceride → anaplerosis. metabolic rescue paradigm.
5. **mitochondrial replacement therapy (MRT) UK 2015** = 3-parent IVF Newcastle. mt-DNA germline replacement. ethical + regulatory 한정 — UK only (US/EU 다수 금지).
6. **CoQ10 + ubiquinol + idebenone supplement** = 미토콘드리아 일반 보충 first-line. evidence-base 일관 부족 + heterogeneous response.
7. **NAD+ NR/NMN + urolithin A Mitopure + mitoQ** = 노화-mitochondria crosstalk supplement (cross-aging). RCT 부족 + 보충제 시장 일반.
8. **DCA dichloroacetate + bezafibrate + vatiquinone** = research-grade. PDH 활성화 + PPAR + Friedreich. 임상 trial 진행.
9. **AAV9 + mt-DNA targeted gene therapy + iPSC mitochondrial transplantation** = research-grade. heteroplasmy + germline + ethical 한정.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, mitochondrial 임상 의미 한정 (heterogeneous + 1:5,000 prevalence rare).

